\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\sa120\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\insrsid6771226 The issue of languages is often a tricky one. The role of language is near and dear to many people\rquote s hearts, and there are a number of ways they can be treated. 
\par When using broad skills, the Languages skill measures what languages the player knows: each rank over mediocre equates to one language when play begins. When using general skills, Languages are split into Linguistics (spoken
