\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\sb120\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\b\i\f184\insrsid6771226 General Combat Skill options
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\sa120\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\insrsid6771226 Any of these three options can work as broad combat skills. No one option is r
